    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1954-06-27T04:07:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1954-06-27T04:07:00-05:00" n="242"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d242">
                <head>242. Telegram From <gloss type="from">
                        <gloss target="#t_PBSPBSUCCESS1">PBSUCCESS</gloss> Headquarters in
                        Florida</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">
                        <gloss target="#t_CIA1">CIA</gloss> Station</gloss> in [<hi rend="italic"
                        >place not declassified</hi>]<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d242fn1"
                        >Source: Central Intelligence Agency, Job 79–01025A, Box 148, Folder 2.
                        Secret; Priority; RYBAT; <gloss target="#t_PBSPBSUCCESS1">PBSUCCESS</gloss>.
                        Repeated to the Director of Central Intelligence.</note>
                </head>
                <dateline>[<hi rend="italic">place not declassified</hi>], <date
                        calendar="gregorian" when="1954-06-27T09:07:00+00:00">June 27, 1954,
                        0907Z</date>.</dateline>
                <p>4421. For <persName corresp="#p_OMH1">Ontrich</persName>. Following received from
                        [<hi rend="italic">place not declassified</hi>]:</p>
                <p>“ERRATIC refuses join <persName corresp="#p_CJH1">Calligeris</persName> as he
                    states invasion plan being followed contrary his recommendations and
                    convictions. Further, does not see how he could help at Esquipulas at
                    present.</p>
                <p>Is recommending to followers in <gloss target="#t_DTFROGS1">DTFROGS</gloss> they
                    proceed via <gloss target="#t_WSHOOFS1">WSHOOFS</gloss> to aid <persName
                        corresp="#p_CJH1">Calligeris</persName>.</p>
                <p>Is sending [<hi rend="italic">name not declassified</hi>] to <gloss
                        target="#t_WSHOOFS1">WSHOOFS</gloss> soon to contact <persName
                        corresp="#p_CJH1">Calligeris</persName> organization. [<hi rend="italic"
                        >name not declassified</hi>] just arrived from <gloss target="#t_WSBURNT1"
                        >WSBURNT</gloss> with intel info. [<hi rend="italic">1 line of source text
                        not declassified</hi>]”</p>
            </div>
        </body>
